Provides inference based on the survey package for the wide range of parametric models in the 'VGAM' package.

name: r-svyvgam
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '1.2' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-svyvgam
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/svyVGAM_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/svyVGAM/svyVGAM_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 108c418f6207906cdc5877f41e77e3d6694467e7afcc0e843c4d7651ae38c307

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
    - cross-r-base {{ r_base }}    # [build_platform != target_platform]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-vgam
    - r-survey
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-vgam
    - r-survey

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('svyVGAM')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('svyVGAM')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=svyVGAM
  license: GPL-3.0-only
  summary: Provides inference based on the survey package for the wide range of parametric models
    in the 'VGAM' package.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file:
    - '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - vitodelgrec

# Package: svyVGAM
